<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtsensors-rotationsensor.xml">RotationSensor</db:link> element reports on device rotation around the X, Y and Z axes.</db:para>
<db:para>This element wraps the <db:link xlink:href="qrotationsensor.xml">QRotationSensor</db:link> class. Please see the documentation for <db:link xlink:href="qrotationsensor.xml">QRotationSensor</db:link> for details.</db:para>
